content.query:
SELECT *
FROM OPENROWSET(
   BULK 'https://lwscusdevdfcicddl.dfs.core.windows.net/yellowtaxidata/yellow_tripdata_2023-01.parquet',
   FORMAT = 'PARQUET',
   WITH (
       pickup_datetime DATETIME,
       dropoff_datetime DATETIME,
       passenger_count INT,
       trip_distance FLOAT,
       fare_amount MONEY
   )
) AS [Result];
